sources.description:
She Must Save Her Town Before Christmas | A Christmas Proposal | Christmas Romance Movie - A local attorney returns to her small hometown just as plans emerge to demolish the cherished ski resort that has been the heart of the community for generations. To save the town, she must face off against her charming but determined ex-boyfriend, who is leading the demolition efforts. Amid holiday festivities, falling snow, and unexpected romance, she discovers that fighting for the town might also mean rediscovering love, hope, and the true spirit of Christmas.

2021.  Stars: Nicole Eggert, David O'Donnell, Tom Arnold
